      <li>
        <p><strong>Languages:</strong> GCC C/C++, Java, C#, Python, TypeScript, PureScript, Haskell, SQL</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p><strong>Frameworks:</strong> GNU Make, SpringBoot, Maven, .NET, React, Tailwind</p>
